<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/69189833-heather-morris"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1502062618i/69189833._UX100_CR0,16,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
