<span id="freeTextContainer3593759811738459330">As with all holocaust stories, my heart hurts. It bleeds for all those who suffered and still shocks me. <br/>But the survivors and the hope is unbelievably real. How anyone ever recovers, I will never know. Forgiveness and healing are themselves a miracle and Each story as necessary and precious as the next.<br/><br/>Thank you, Lale, for sharing yours. 4.5⭐️</span>

